node.text:
The Yick Cheong Building in Hong Kong 🏬
This building is separated into five blocks, which consist of about 2243 apartments with  approximately 10,000 people living inside. Would you live here? 🤯
Video by: @trystane
Location: Quarry Bay, Hong Kong 🇭🇰

node.text:
The gypset atlas doesn't look like a normal map . Instead of metropolises like London, Shanghai and New York, the capitals of our world are small, out - of the way towns. Syntopia is the perfect place to reconnect with nature, culture and people.. Close your eyes and picture yourself here 🌵 #thesyntopia #thesyntopialife
Location: @thesyntopia 
.
Photos by: @aris_katsigiannis @ariszita & @the_globbers @asiminaa
